targets.expr: (((count(count(node_cpu_seconds_total{job="$job_node_exporter", instance="$instance"}) by (cpu))) - avg(sum by (mode)(irate(node_cpu_seconds_total{job="$job_node_exporter", mode="idle",instance=~"$instance"}[1m])))) * 100) / count(count(node_cpu_seconds_total{job="$job_node_exporter", instance=~"$instance"}) by (cpu))
